                        AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner
                    </a>
                </td>
                <td class="col-3 col-sm-2 col-xl-3">
                    <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/certification/certified-cloud-practitioner/" target="_blank">
                        <img src="~/img/aws-cp-tag.png" class="img-fluid" alt="aws cp certification badge" />
                    </a>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
